<u class="+ topic/ph hi-d/u ">Calibration step</u> 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">This warning is generated during the calibration step "MediaX" which is part of the Media-calibration sequences.
</p></section><section id="GUID-5AC5D3D0-AC77-4791-AD77-40B50785DD16" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title "> 
