</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Type
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">ToDo
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remarks
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">1
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Decision
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Check whether clean media is used
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">2
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Clean the media using IPA or cut the polluted part of the media
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">3
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Decision
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Check whether the correct profile is selected
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">4
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Select correct profile or download correct profile.
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Download profile from GraphiPlaza
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">5
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Decision
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Check whether this error is also present when using other media.
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">6
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Use other media
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> The media is not suitable for the Colorado printers.
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">7
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Decision
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Check whether the M&amp;C-scanner needs to be cleaned
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">8
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Clean the glass-window of the M&amp;C-scanner using IPA.
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">9
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Decision
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Check whether the printed pattern look complete (no deviation droplets)
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> See example top of this page
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">10
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Perform manual maintenance on the printheads.
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">11
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Replace the printhead
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><xref href="GUID-915F84BE-7881-400A-A351-FF4DB79FE9B0" class="- topic/xref "/>
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">12
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Check the M&amp;C-scanner
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><xref href="GUID-17F448B7-8A72-45B1-B56D-FC5C0BE28701.xml" class="- topic/xref " type="task"><?ditaot gentext?>05-6-017 M&amp;C scanner test [Special Tests]</xref>
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">13
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Replace the M&amp;C-scanner
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><xref href="GUID-563F9EBE-CC03-4CAA-93C8-8AA3AB9B162B.xml" class="- topic/xref " type="task"><?ditaot gentext?>05 How to remove the Measurement &amp; Control (M&amp;C) unit</xref>
</p></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section><section id="GUID-6D84DFCF-0714-4019-ABFB-68423C0D84FC" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title "> 
<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b "> Evaluate/Prevention</b> </title><p class="- topic/p ">Use prescribed materials.
</p></section><section id="GUID-18BBB4BD-9BC7-46AF-A9DD-E504C2B2CAC6" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title "> 
<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b "> Background info</b> </title><p class="- topic/p ">During media-calibration the media-step markers are measured by the M&amp;C-scanner. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">In case these markers cannot be measured correctly the calibration step fails. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">In most cases this is caused by media profiles that are not set correctly or media that is not suitable for the Colorado-family.
</p></section></taskbody><related-links class="- topic/related-links "><linkpool class="- topic/linkpool " mapkeyref="GUID-8A41CFEA-5928-4042-A2CB-507A5D034160"><link class="- topic/link " mapclass="- map/topicref " format="dita" type="concept" href="generated-topic-GUID-12A22F29-4989-4601-A883-7BC951F448D2.xml" role="parent"><?ditaot usertext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext "><?ditaot usertext?>Diagnostics</linktext></link></linkpool></related-links>
